{
  "stem": "18470.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 16.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think I told you also that, actually, I wouldn't be talking to you altogether were it not for a righteous man who happened to have been a policeman, who warned my father by sending his son to tell him that there was a warrant out for his arrest that day, and that he should immediately leave the city.",
      "word_count": 59
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, the-- [SIGHS] the warrant was out for his arrest because [BACKROUND NOISE] he had an incident that occurred when we went into the back woods with horse and chaise, and-- the kid to whom my father was visiting his home, threw a bucket of water on the horse, because the horse was a Jewish horse.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the horse was, of course, shocked by the bucket of water.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my father took the kid by the earlobe, and marched him into the store of his father's house.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then his father gave him a good whack.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the fact was that my father had hit a child in a Hitlerjugend uniform.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A Hitler Youth uniform, which meant that he had committed a serious crime.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And upon this kid reporting what had happened to him, a warrant went out for my father's arrest.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was posted.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now the town hall, as I understood it, had also the SS, the SA, the local police, and the state police all there together.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the local policeman happened to have seen the warrant posted, the arrest warrant, and he sent his son to warn my dad.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my father left overnight on a flatboat down to Holland.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he lived in Amsterdam for a period of about eight months.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They would have arrested him, and they probably would have beaten him to death for having put a hand onto a Hitlerjugend uniform.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
